To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

I am writing to request access to any and all tax records and filings related to the Church of Scientology for the years 2010 through 2020. The Church of Scientology is a religious organization that has been controversial in the past and has been the subject of media scrutiny. I am interested in reviewing the tax records to gain a better understanding of the organization's finances and to help inform public discourse on this issue.

Specifically, I am requesting access to the following documents:

Form 990, Return of Organization Exempt from Income Tax, for the years 2010-2020
Form 1023, Application for Recognition of Exemption Under Section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code, and any subsequent correspondence related to the Church of Scientology's tax-exempt status
Any correspondence, audit reports, or other documents related to the Church of Scientology's tax-exempt status or tax filings for the years 2010-2020

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Jordan

To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Junaid Hussain, also known as TeaMp0isoN. Specifically, I am seeking any records related to Mr. Hussain that the FBI may have in its possession.

To assist in your search, I would like to provide a brief summary of Mr. Hussain's background. Junaid Hussain was a British citizen who was believed to have been a prominent member of the ISIS terror network. Mr. Hussain was reportedly involved in several high-profile attacks and cyber operations, including the hacking of the US Central Command's Twitter account in 2015. Mr. Hussain's Twitter handle was @teamp0isoned. Mr. Hussain was reportedly killed in a US drone strike in Syria in August 2015.

I am requesting any and all records related to Mr. Hussain that the FBI may have, including but not limited to:

Investigative reports
Correspondence with other law enforcement agencies or intelligence agencies regarding Mr. Hussain
Surveillance records
Arrest records
Any other records related to Mr. Hussain
In addition, I am requesting any records related to inter-agency correspondence regarding Mr. Hussain. This includes any records related to discussions or exchanges of information between the FBI and other law enforcement agencies or intelligence agencies regarding Mr. Hussain.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Jordan
